OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 14 MAY
OL,4,CEVENTS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1976FPeter Woods is taken off the air
OL,7,Fas he reads the opening headlines on
OL,8,FNewsday (BBC Two).
OL,9,
OL,10,FHe is sent home and replaced as
OL,11,Fpresenter of Newsnight later that
OL,12,Fevening on BBC Two.
OL,13,
OL,14,FViewers complained that Woods appeared
OL,15,Fto be drunk, as his speech was slurred.
OL,16,FThe official line from the BBC was that
OL,17,Fhe had suffered a reaction to
OL,18,Fmedication.
OL,19,
OL,20,CG2005FJohn Inverdale presents Rugby
OL,21,FSpecial (BBC Two) for the final time.
